ygData.msgSnippet: Who would win? That really depends on the player and the equipment. I ve trashed a level 35 wiz with pet using my 20 war, I got very close to killing a 47
ygData.messageBody:
Who would win? That really depends on the player and the equipment.
I've trashed a level 35 wiz with pet using my 20 war, I got very
close to killing a 47 ranger with my 22 rogue, and back when I was
34, I took out a 40 wiz. Assuming that both are using pets, nukes and
dots, I would think the necro should end up winning. Use your
lifespike/tap what ever to harm your opponent and heal yourself.
That's the one advantage he won't have.

Timmye Cousteau
41 Druid
The Rathe
